{
  "id": "RAW_4a9693a9",
  "title": "声画合一，一镜入戏 | 豆包视频生成模型 Seedance 1.5 Pro 终于来了",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzkwMzY5NzU2Nw==&mid=2247488510&idx=1&sn=1fd7337168cdf28d1427631d265b13e9",
  "date": "2025-12-18 05:10:00",
  "author": "有机大橘子",
  "siteName": "有机大橘子",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100004859\" data-ratio=\"0.42407407407407405\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=5477ed72&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbyNSHXBoYpdsNtGkFtGmXsSUX9ECHwVWP01z5RySibuvEjicUUllVoRlHj9Q6M1MNgLd6IrV64D2tbzTMSNu0gCw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\" data-pm-slice=\"0 0 []\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Veo3 和 Sora2 发布之后，AI 视频模型的发展趋势已经非常清晰，就是是音视频融合，以前「视频归视频，声音归声音」，未来画面、配音、音效都是一次完成。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">今天，火山引擎正式发布了新一代视频创作模型&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Seedance 1.5 pro</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。它采用了业界领先的</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">音视频联合生成方案。</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">画面与声音在同一时间维度上自然生长。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">为了验证它的真实实力，我拿到模型后进行了一系列高难度的测试，从方言口音到 3A 游戏音效，从微表情演技到电影级运镜，看看它是否真的能做到“声画俱全”。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 16px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">(注：本次实测总体“抽卡”成功率约为 50%，由于公众号只能放10个视频，以下展示均为成功案例)</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">一、 听得懂“乡音”：相声和方言能力测试</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Seedance 1.5 pro 宣称支持多语言及方言。我没有测试普通说话场景，直接挑战相声和方言。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">传统中式茶馆风格，背景是屏风和观众虚影。 人物： 两位身穿长大褂的相声演员站在桌子后。 动作与语音序列： 逗哏（右边穿黑大褂）： 面带自信微笑，手拿折扇，深吸一口气，开始表演极速贯口：“我请您吃：蒸羊羔、蒸熊掌、蒸鹿尾儿、烧花鸭、烧雏鸡、烧子鹅、卤猪、卤鸭、酱鸡、腊肉、松花小肚儿……” 捧哏（左边穿灰大褂）： 侧身看着逗哏，时不时点头，在间隙插话：“好！”、“嚯！”、“听着这就香！” 音效： 逗哏语速极快且清晰的北京话，捧哏的衬托声，以及茶馆里观众的叫好声和掌声。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">电影感实拍，夜晚喧闹的成都火锅店，热气腾腾。特写镜头对准一位扎着丸子头的年轻女孩，她满脸通红，一边用手扇风一边夹起一块毛肚。她用</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">四川话</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">大声说道：“哎呀，这个火锅好巴适哦！就是太辣了，老板儿，再来一唯怡豆奶嘛！” 背景音是嘈杂的人声和火锅沸腾的咕嘟声。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">港风复古滤镜，拥挤的茶餐厅，绿色马赛克地砖。一位穿着白背心的大叔正在喝冻柠茶，表情夸张地对镜头用</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">粤语</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">抱怨：“哇，依家啲后生仔真系唔捱得苦架，叫佢做少少野就话辛苦！” 背景有碗筷碰撞声和茶餐厅特有的喧哗声。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">纪实摄影风格，阳光斑驳的北京老胡同，红墙灰瓦。 画面： 一位穿着白色背心、手拿蒲扇的老大爷，另一只手提着一个精致的鸟笼。 动作与声音： 他慢悠悠地转过身，对着镜头挑了挑眉毛，用地道的北京话（儿化音极重） 说道：“您猜怎么着？今儿个天儿不错，这就叫地道！您听听这鸟叫唤的，倍儿脆！” 音效： 远处的鸽哨声、自行车的铃铛声、知了叫声。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">电影《黄土地》风格，黄土高原沟壑纵横，强烈的西北日光。 画面： 一位头上包着白毛巾的老汉，蹲在窑洞门口，手里捧着一个巨大的海碗（比脸还大），里面是宽宽的油泼面。 动作与声音： 他大口吸溜了一口面，抬起头，满嘴是油，用陕西话憨厚地感叹：“额滴神啊，这面做得太香咧！嘹咋咧！” 音效： 巨大的吸溜面条声（Slurping）、风吹过黄土坡的声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">方言音画小结：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">当模型学会了方言之后，人物的表演更加真实可信，最初的几次尝试充满了惊喜感。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">不过测试中也发现了一些模型的盲区。比如模型的上海话不太地道；</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">而令人很意外的是，互联网语料极丰富的东北话，模型竟然完全不会。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">看来模型在特定方言数据的覆盖上仍有不少优化空间。</span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">二、 听得见“质感”：精准音效测试</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">除了人声，环境音效（SFX）与画面的同步率也非常重要，可以简化以前复杂的 AI 音效工作流。特别是在游戏场景、电影特效场景等有高频音效需求的场景里。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">UE5 引擎渲染，3A 级暗黑奇幻大作风格，4K 极致画质，光线追踪开启。 场景： 暴风雨中的古堡废墟，一只体型遮天蔽日的黑鳞巨龙盘踞在断壁残垣之上，双眼闪烁着凶光。 动作与音效序列（严丝合缝）： 威慑： 巨龙压低身体，利爪深深嵌入石砖（音效：岩石碎裂的咔嚓声），喉咙里发出威胁性的低吼（音效：低沉的、引起胸腔共鸣的“呼噜”声）。 蓄力： 巨龙猛然吸气，颈部鳞片缝隙透出熔岩般的红光（音效：尖锐的气流吸入声，伴随能量积蓄的嗡嗡声）。 释放： 巨龙张开血盆大口，向镜头喷出漫天烈焰（音效：震耳欲聋的爆裂咆哮，紧接着是烈火喷涌的“呼啸”声和燃烧的噼啪声）。 环境音： 远处的雷声滚滚，雨点打在龙鳞上的细碎声音。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">三、 懂镜头语言：运镜与动态张力</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Seedance 1.5 pro 不仅懂画面声音，还懂专业的摄影术语，在运镜上表现得更加专业，连续性更好。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">赛博朋克霓虹城市，雨夜。一辆重型摩托车在高速公路上疾驰。镜头首先进行</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">长镜头跟随</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">，紧贴摩托车后轮，捕捉溅起的水花。随后镜头快速拉升并旋转到车手正面，执行</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">希区柯克变焦（Dolly Zoom）</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">，背景的城市灯光极速后退压缩，展现速度带来的眩晕感。背景音是轰鸣的引擎声和合成器电子乐。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">王家卫电影美学，高对比度，霓虹灯绿与暖黄交错，略带胶片颗粒感，手持晃动镜头。 镜头 1： 透过便利店布满雨水的玻璃窗拍摄，店内货架虚化，霓虹灯光斑驳。 镜头 2： 慢动作（抽帧效果），一位穿着风衣的男子在货架前拿起一个凤梨罐头，眼神迷离忧郁。 镜头 3： 特写男子的侧脸，他看着罐头底部的日期，对着空气自言自语（内心独白混响）：“不知道从什么时候开始，什么东西上面都有个日期，连保鲜膜都会过期。” 音效： 淅沥沥的雨声，远处模糊的警笛声，以及低沉忧伤的大提琴配乐。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">四、 演得真切：细腻的人物表演</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">AI 视频最难攻克的堡垒是“演技”，尤其是微表情和多人互动。在这方面 Seedance 1.5 Pro 模型也有了进步，在部分场景的表现相当细腻，再配合精准的声音，能带来很强的代入感。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">电影感实拍，深夜暴雨，车窗上布满流下的雨水，窗外模糊的路灯光影在人物脸上交替划过。 人物特写： 驾驶座上一位疲惫的中年女性，双手紧紧抓着方向盘，指节发白。 情绪与动作序列： 压抑（0-2秒）： 她死死咬着下嘴唇，眼眶里蓄满了泪水，身体随着呼吸剧烈起伏，试图忍住不哭（音效：沉重的呼吸声，车顶噼里啪啦的暴雨声，雨刮器的刮擦声）。 崩溃（2-5秒）： 突然，她再也忍不住，猛地砸向方向盘，爆发出一声撕心裂肺的哭喊，眼泪夺眶而出，五官因为痛苦而扭曲（音效：手掌重击皮质方向盘的闷响，紧接着是带有破音的、窒息般的尖叫哭声，掩盖了雨声）。 余韵（5-7秒）： 她无力地靠在椅背上，大口喘气，眼神空洞（音效：哭声转为抽泣，雨声重新占据主导）。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">五、 讲好故事：连续镜头切换</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">在连续镜头切换场景的测试中，模型展现了优秀的“剪辑思维”。多镜头的流畅衔接，从远景到特写，叙事逻辑清晰，配乐与画面风格高度统一。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 8px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:1em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">韦斯·安德森电影风格，极致的中心对称构图，粉色与青色的糖果色调，平光照明。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">镜头 1：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;远景，一座孤独耸立在悬崖边的红白条纹灯塔，海鸥在天上定格般飞翔。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">镜头 2：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;快速切至室内中景，一个留着八字胡、戴着红色针织帽的看守人，面无表情地坐在桌前，桌上放着一个巨大的黄色包裹。&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">镜头 3：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;特写，看守人机械地撕开包裹（夸张的撕纸声），里面是一只戴着墨镜的橘猫。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">镜头 4：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;看守人抬头直视镜头，用毫无起伏的语调说：“</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">这确实是个惊喜。</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">”&nbsp;</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">音效：</span></span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\" style=\"font-size: 14px;color: rgb(122, 79, 214);\">&nbsp;背景音乐是轻快的拨弦古键琴（Harpsichord），配合海浪声和海鸥叫声。</span></span></p>\n  <p nodeleaf=\"\"></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">六、 背后的技术</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">Seedance 1.5 pro</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在技术上和前代模型的本质区别在于它</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">不再把声音看作视频的附属品</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">通过 MMDiT 原生架构和针对音视频联合场景的 RLHF 训练，它解决了以往 AI 视频“画质虽好但无神、无声、无镜头感”的痛点，特别是在中文方言和专业摄影控制上形成了差异化竞争优势。</span></span></p>\n  <p style=\"text-align: center;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-imgfileid=\"100004855\" data-ratio=\"0.3592592592592593\" data-s=\"300,640\" type=\"block\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a4161d94&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FbyNSHXBoYpdsNtGkFtGmXsSUX9ECHwVWYezwte9Abm0cHA7pjwEI9utsHdcgyibOUU59spLjeIFqlqNticl0EJfQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng%26from%3Dappmsg\"></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">一些架构设计特点：</span></span></p>\n  <ol style=\"font-style: normal;font-variant-ligatures: normal;font-variant-caps: normal;font-weight: 400;letter-spacing: normal;orphans: 2;text-align: start;text-indent: 0px;text-transform: none;widows: 2;word-spacing: 0px;-webkit-text-stroke-width: 0px;white-space: normal;text-decoration-thickness: initial;text-decoration-style: initial;text-decoration-color: initial;list-style: none;color: rgb(20, 86, 240);font-family: &quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;font-size: 15px;line-height: 30px;padding-left: 0px;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">1.&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">基于 MMDiT（Multi-modal Diffusion Transformer） 架构。它采用双分支（Dual-branch）设计，内部集成了一个跨模态联合模块（Cross-modal joint module）。这使得视觉和听觉流在生成过程中就能进行深度交互，确保了极高的时间同步性和语义一致性。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">2.&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">引入音频反馈的 RLHF。在 SFT 之上，专门针对音视频上下文开发了强化学习（RLHF）算法。它使用多维奖励模型来评估视频质量、美学表现以及音频保真度。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">3.&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">推理流水线。它的推理链条包括：</span></span><span style=\"border:1px solid rgb(222, 224, 227);border-radius:4px;padding:1px 2px;margin:0px 3px;\"><span leaf=\"\">用户提示词 -&gt; 提示词工程 -&gt; 文本编码器 -&gt; 联合生成模型(DiT) -&gt; 视频/音频细化器(Refiner) -&gt; 输出</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n   <li>\n    <p><span leaf=\"\">4.&nbsp;</span><span><span leaf=\"\">评估标准：升级了评测基准，不仅看画质，还专门增加了“视频生动性”维度（分为动作和镜头两个子维度）以及四个音频维度（指令遵循、音质、音画同步、音频表现力）。</span></span></p>\n   </li>\n  </ol>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">完整技术报告地址：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><a href=\"https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.13507\" target=\"_blank\">https://arxiv.org/pdf/2512.13507</a></span></span></span></p>\n  <h3 style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;white-space:normal;font-weight:bold;letter-spacing:0.578px;font-size:20px;padding-bottom:12px;text-decoration-style:initial;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;margin-top:0px;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;margin-bottom:8px;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">七、 总结与体验入口</span></span></h3>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">Seedance 1.5 pro 是 AI 视频生成从“默片时代”迈向“有声电影时代”的重要一步。它在音画同步、方言演绎、运镜控制和叙事表达上展现了惊人的潜力。虽然目前在部分方言支持（如东北话、上海话）和复杂场景的稳定性（抽卡成功率约 50%）上仍有提升空间，但它已经能够辅助创作者完成短剧、广告 demo 甚至电影分镜的制作。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">体验入口：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span><span leaf=\"\">目前 Seedance 1.5 Pro 已正式上线，可以在这几个地方玩到：</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">即梦 AI ：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;网页端选择“视频生成” -&gt; 模型选择&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">视频 3.5 Pro</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">豆包 App：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;对话框输入“照片动起来” -&gt; 上传照片 -&gt; 选择&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">1.5 Pro</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;模型（内测中）。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:left;\"><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">开发者 API：</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;下周</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">，Seedance 1.5 Pro 模型 API 将在&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-weight:bold;\"><span leaf=\"\">火山引擎 (Volcano Engine)</span></span><span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;开放调用。现在可到火山方舟体验中心体验模型效果，也可预约模型服务。</span></span></p>\n  <p data-author=\"dui!\" style=\"-webkit-text-stroke-width:0px;font-variant-caps:normal;margin:0px 0px 4px;white-space:normal;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:normal;font-size:15px;text-decoration-style:initial;line-height:2em;min-height:20px;font-style:normal;text-decoration-thickness:initial;text-transform:none;word-spacing:0px;text-indent:0px;word-break:break-all;font-family:&quot;PingFang SC&quot;, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, &quot;Helvetica Neue&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei UI&quot;, &quot;Microsoft YaHei&quot;, Arial, sans-serif;orphans:2;text-decoration-color:initial;font-variant-ligatures:normal;widows:2;text-align:start;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(51, 109, 244);\"><span leaf=\"\"><a href=\"https://exp.volcengine.com/ark/vision?launch=seedance\" target=\"_blank\">https://exp.volcengine.com/ark/vision?launch=seedance</a></span></span></p>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "豆包视频生成模型 Seedance 1.5 Pro 通过音视频联合生成方案，实现了方言、音效、运镜和人物表演的声画高度同步与专业控制，标志着 AI 视频从“默片”走向“有声电影”时代。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "豆包视频生成模型 Seedance 1.5 Pro 通过音视频联合生成方案，实现了方言、音效、运镜和人物表演的声画高度同步与专业控制，标志着 AI 视频从“默片”走向“有声电影”时代。",
  "summary": "文章详细介绍了火山引擎最新发布的视频生成模型 Seedance 1.5 Pro 的核心技术和卓越能力。该模型采用 MMDiT 原生架构和音视频联合生成方案，解决了传统 AI 视频在声画同步、情感表达和专业运镜上的不足。通过对方言、3A 游戏音效、电影级运镜和微表情演技等高难度测试，Seedance 1.5 Pro 展现出强大的“声画合一”能力，尤其在中文方言和专业摄影控制方面具有差异化优势。文章还深入探讨了其技术架构，包括双分支 MMDiT 设计、引入音频反馈的 RLHF 训练和精密的推理流水线，并提及模型在特定方言覆盖和抽卡成功率上仍有提升空间。最后提供了即梦 AI、豆包 App 和开发者 API 等体验入口，指出其在短剧、广告和电影分镜制作中的巨大潜力。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "Seedance 1.5 Pro 实现音视频联合生成，告别传统 AI 视频“默片”时代。",
      "explanation": "模型通过原生架构将画面、配音、音效一次完成，解决了声画分离的痛点，提升了视频生成的真实感和沉浸感。"
    },
    {
      "point": "模型具备强大的中文方言和专业音效生成能力。",
      "explanation": "通过对方言相声、地方特色情景和 3A 游戏音效的测试，模型能精准识别并生成地道的方言口音和高品质的环境音效，极大地丰富了视频表现力。"
    },
